00:11:17.892 --> 00:11:21.792
sort of getting a random disoriented bunch of cells and you're cutting through it.

198
00:11:22.792 --> 00:11:25.092
Okay? So you don't really have an orientation, an up, a down.

199
00:11:25.452 --> 00:11:28.772
You're just sort of cutting directly a small section through the tumor.

200
00:11:28.812 --> 00:11:32.652
So if you're trying to track nerves in that tumor, it's not so simple.

201
00:11:34.892 --> 00:11:38.672
Now, imagine that you have a single cell, so this is just sort of to represent a

