00:16:03.648 --> 00:16:05.458
reality of the type of technologies that we're using.

286
00:16:06.008 --> 00:16:09.887
And how do you then attribute those different signals from cells that are in

287
00:16:09.928 --> 00:16:11.068
or out of that plane?

