00:19:18.620 --> 00:19:22.240
called that cell. So this is just one approach, but it's got sort of ranked in

346
00:19:22.280 --> 00:19:23.080
that type of

347
00:19:26.820 --> 00:19:30.500
logic where it's sort of got a flow cytometry type of

348
00:19:30.520 --> 00:19:30.900
background.

349
00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:36.240
Here's just an example of a picture of taking a raw staining, and this is of a

