00:21:21.120 --> 00:21:23.880
And again, these cells are really, really densely packed up next to each other, so

381
00:21:23.900 --> 00:21:27.160
it's not so simple to just-- it's not like you're doing this in cell culture where

382
00:21:27.180 --> 00:21:30.680
you have these massive boundary or barriers or spaces between these different

