00:22:34.020 --> 00:22:35.930
work and benchmark them against each other.

403
00:22:35.940 --> 00:22:38.460
And they're really, really phenomenal in terms of cleaning up some of these data

404
00:22:38.560 --> 00:22:42.220
sets to more accurately define the immune microenvironment within the spatial

405
00:22:42.560 --> 00:22:43.030
context.

